text: Catocala carissima, the carissima underwing, is a moth of the family Erebidae. The species can be found from Florida through Georgia to Texas. It was formerly considered to be a subspecies of Catocala cara. ==References== ==External links== * Catocala cara carissima info carissima Category:Moths described in 1880 Category:Moths of North America
